[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
=======================================================
Modify your `/etc/rc.conf` by adding these settings

qemu_guest_agent_enable="YES"
qemu_guest_agent_flags="-d -v -l /var/log/qemu-ga.log"

and run
# service qemu-guest-agent start

For detailed help use `qemu-ga -h`
=======================================================
EOM
}
]
